The best place to enjoy desserts and cakes

Located for over 20 years in Singapore, our bakery is one of the greatest places to enjoy desserts and cakes

About us

Making a variety of baked goods which might include bread and pastries. They are responsible for following recipes, measuring and mixing ingredients, and baking items. Bakers work with various kinds of equipment which include ovens and mixers. This profession is quite physical as they knead, roll, cut, and shape dough while moving ingredients around the facility. Finally, depending on the establishment they work in some bakers may be responsible for serving customers and taking orders

Today's specials

Every day our chef prepares special desserts. Here is what is on the menu for today.

item.title: About
item.dc:creator: kaungkhantnaing
item.content:encoded:
About Us

Our Story

Making a variety of baked goods which might include bread and pastries. They are responsible for following recipes, measuring and mixing ingredients, and baking items. Bakers work with various kinds of equipment which include ovens and mixers. This profession is quite physical as they knead, roll, cut, and shape dough while moving ingredients around the facility. Finally, depending on the establishment they work in some bakers may be responsible for serving customers and taking orders. I am the owner of SEASON. Bragging on my new bakery, great location near Willows Shopping Centre. I am an artisan-baker and I trained in Paris.

Our values

Quality- To establish and maintain high-quality standards in services and products, and be curious in seeking improvement.

Value - To create value beyond customer expectations.

Mission - Our mission is to make, distribute and sell the finest quality all natureal desserts and fresh cakes.

For a light lunch, we would also serve cafe.

"SEASON has the best cheesecake I’ve ever had. Always fresh, and melts in the mouth. Would Recommend Highly"

Barry

Website Explanation
